{
  "char_id": "char_66ff5e94",
  "char_name": "芙宁娜",
  "items": [
    {
      "id": 179,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_179_3a6a.wav",
      "text": "待战在那里做什么?该不会是因为过于激动,说不出话了吧?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "轻蔑嘲讽",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.65
    },
    {
      "id": 180,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_2_1_664a.wav",
      "text": "哼,没错,站在你面前的就是风单人人皆知的大明星,弗宁娜哦。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "骄傲自得",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 7.93
    },
    {
      "id": 181,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_2_2_2abe.wav",
      "text": "哼,我的档期可是很緊的,能約到我,說明你運氣不錯嘛",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "得意炫耀",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.32
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0003.wav",
      "text": "茶会是淑女的必修课,如果你想学习茶会礼仪的话,我可以教你哦。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "优雅邀请",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.87
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0004.wav",
      "text": "哎,好无聊啊。没有什么更有趣的事吗?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "无聊烦躁",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.01
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0005.wav",
      "text": "唉,人气太高也是一种苦恼,谁让我这么受欢迎呢?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "得意炫耀",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.5
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0006.wav",
      "text": "好大的雨,等等,水应该不会淹上来吧?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "担忧不安",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.53
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0007.wav",
      "text": "哇,这地方很适合阴影取景!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋发现",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0008.wav",
      "text": "这阳光的热度都快赶上我平时用的影视灯了,还好太阳只有一个。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "轻松调侃",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "id": 182,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_182_00b4.wav",
      "text": "风中传来不安的低语。那是被遗忘的海兽,做噩梦时的梦意。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "阴森不安",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.3
    },
    {
      "id": 183,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_183_bbd3.wav",
      "text": "你问为什么是做噩梦?呃,因为,恐惧感是会向外传递的?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "困惑迟疑",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 7.29
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0016.wav",
      "text": "真是一片荒芜的景象,让我赐予你们水的恩泽吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "庄严宣告",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.79
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0017.wav",
      "text": "嗯,早安,哇,需要起这么早吗?再多睡一会儿也没关系吧?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "惊讶关切",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 9.05
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0018.wav",
      "text": "晚安,我的蛋糕在哪里?哦,什么什么,你说早上刚吃过?那已经隔了好久了!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "撒娇抱怨",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 9.43
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0020.wav",
      "text": "唉,切贝雷达小姐最近总嘀咕着减肥,还说要拉上我一起,哼,比起上个月,我肚子都瘦了一圈还不止呢,我已经很努力在控制体态了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "无奈抱怨",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 14.0
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0021.wav",
      "text": "喂,你,看得出来吗?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静询问",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0022.wav",
      "text": "呼,正好我也困了。明天见,记得准时叫我起来。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "慵懒平和",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 7.13
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0023.wav",
      "text": "你问我参加茶会的这几个小家伙?他们可是我忠实的追随者。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自豪得意",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.49
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0024.wav",
      "text": "今天就破例为你介绍一下吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "轻松愉悦",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "id": 184,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_25_1_dc38.wav",
      "text": "这位是谢贝雷达小姐最可爱的女仆",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "中性介绍",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.85
    },
    {
      "id": 185,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_25_2_4c92.wav",
      "text": "虽然有时会不小心捡坏我的衣服",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "无奈抱怨",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0026.wav",
      "text": "这位是海威马夫人,可靠的管理人,将我的生活打理得井井有条。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静赞许",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.8
    },
    {
      "id": 186,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_27_1_8666.wav",
      "text": "最后这位喜欢说教的是乌色勋爵,负责一切礼仪相关的事情。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "客观介绍",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.41
    },
    {
      "id": 187,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_27_2_04c5.wav",
      "text": "哼哼,虽然我已允许你参加我的茶会,但想要得到他们的认可,你还要多多努力才行。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "轻蔑施压",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 8.26
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0028.wav",
      "text": "我对自己的歌唱水平还是很有自信的,不过值得我开口唱颂的段落可不多。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "自信淡然",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.42
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0029.wav",
      "text": "希望那些剧团里的创作者们加把劲,不要让我等太久。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "不耐烦催促",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.07
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0031.wav",
      "text": "以我们之间的关系,你在我面前无需太过恭敬,可以更随意一些。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "温和亲近",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.83
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0033.wav",
      "text": "你那是什么表情?该不会是想说你从一开始就没有敬仰过我吧?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "怒",
        "complex": "质疑嘲讽",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0034.wav",
      "text": "我的故事已然落幕,接下来开场的是我们的故事了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静期待",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0035.wav",
      "text": "这么说的话,出场费是不是也该翻倍了?好开心哦!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋期待",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 6.05
    },
    {
      "id": 188,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_188_1da9.wav",
      "text": "当那古老的预言终结,一切落幕之后。我曾经陷入很长时间的消沉。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "消沉失落",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.83
    },
    {
      "id": 189,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_189_c271.wav",
      "text": "站在舞台上的人受到观众的追捧。同时,也承受着更多的注视与期待。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "矛盾交织",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.89
    },
    {
      "id": 190,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_190_6e91.wav",
      "text": "但我很清楚,他们期待的并不是我,而是我扮演的那位神明。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "无奈自嘲",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.17
    },
    {
      "id": 191,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_191_d6b9.wav",
      "text": "在这个过程中,我真正得到的只有孤独。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "深沉失落",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0044.wav",
      "text": "所以我一度厌恶任何跟表演有关的事,把自己关在房间里。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "自我封闭",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
      "id": 192,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_192_65b2.wav",
      "text": "直到再次站上舞台,再次面对观众的时候,我才发现。不知不觉,我内心的不安已经消失了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "释然平静",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 8.51
    },
    {
      "id": 193,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_193_0eea.wav",
      "text": "现在的我可以坦然承受他们的目光。也许是因为……我终于开始扮演我自己了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静释然",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 6.99
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0050.wav",
      "text": "丰丹的歌剧经历过几次革新,每次革新都会有许多反对的声音。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "客观陈述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0051.wav",
      "text": "在我印象里,经常有很多人聚在歌剧院吵来吵去,吵得我耳朵嗡嗡响。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "烦躁不耐",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.03
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0052.wav",
      "text": "于是我吓唬他们说,不准再争论这些无关紧要的问题。纳维莱特也顺势敲了一下他的手杖,哥俊渊立刻就安静了。唉,没办法。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "无奈安抚",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 12.14
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0053.wav",
      "text": "我总会不经意间表露出充满威严的一面,希望他们能够理解。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "威严自省",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.25
    },
    {
      "id": 194,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_194_2f54.wav",
      "text": "我很喜欢有光星星。这种生物在无人注视的地方,也能发出自己的光亮,是我心目中最真实的明星。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "赞美向往",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 8.19
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0056.wav",
      "text": "如果有让幽光星星当主角的歌剧就好了,我可以真情实感地在舞台上演绎一只可爱的离群海星。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "憧憬幻想",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 8.09
    },
    {
      "id": 195,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_195_9a2d.wav",
      "text": "琳妮与琳妮特我当然知道。以前我就经常光临他们的演出。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静回忆",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0059.wav",
      "text": "他们的人气虽然高,但跟我比起来还是差了不少。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自信得意",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
      "id": 196,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_60_1_c7d5.wav",
      "text": "由我出场的演出才是真正的座无虚席连站票都卖得干干净净",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "得意炫耀",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "id": 197,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_split_60_2_0e65.wav",
      "text": "至于现在现在我已经退隐了人气下滑也很正常嘛",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "淡然接受",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 8.5
    },
    {
      "id": 198,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_198_62a9.wav",
      "text": "我很感谢纳维莱特这几百年间为丰丹的辛苦付出。他似乎也不打算追究我欺骗民众的罪责。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "欣慰释然",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "id": 199,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_199_1450.wav",
      "text": "反正现在我们已经不需要对接什么工作,我也很久没去墨盲宫了。这对我们双方来说,都是一件好事吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "淡然释怀",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 8.16
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0065.wav",
      "text": "你尝过纳维亚烤的马卡龙吗?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "好奇询问",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0066.wav",
      "text": "不得不承认,她对甜点的造诣已经非常深厚,完全不在我之下,口感和甜度暂且不提,她画在马卡龙上的图案也太可爱了吧,简直就是艺术品,她到底是怎么做到的?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "惊喜赞叹",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 14.65
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0067.wav",
      "text": "难道,真的只是天赋?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "疑惑不解",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0068.wav",
      "text": "我的内心中竟然会产生一种挫败感。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "挫败失落",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0069.wav",
      "text": "下次一定要向他好好打听一下。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "期待好奇",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0070.wav",
      "text": "他是一个很坚强的人。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静陈述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0071.wav",
      "text": "坚强的人不管发生什么,都会很快振作起来,装作没事的样子。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静陈述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0072.wav",
      "text": "这样身边的人就无需背负额外的压力。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平和释然",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0073.wav",
      "text": "我见证过卡雷斯与克洛琳德的决斗。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "冷静叙述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
      "id": 200,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_200_bf75.wav",
      "text": "纳维亚塔在这方面越来越像自己的父亲了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "客观陈述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0077.wav",
      "text": "谁呀,我已经忘掉了,把那么可怕的身影留在脑海中,晚上睡觉都会做噩梦的。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "恐惧不安",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 7.89
    },
    {
      "id": 201,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_201_1274.wav",
      "text": "最近经常见到夏洛蒂忙忙碌碌的身影。他好像很想找我约一期独家专访。哪怕我多次拒绝,她也并不放弃。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静叙述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 7.67
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0081.wav",
      "text": "我本来有点生气的,但是他很坚定地对我说,他希望民众能够了解到一个更加真实的我,也相信民众可以理解我的苦衷。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "释然接纳",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 9.95
    },
    {
      "id": 202,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_202_0e64.wav",
      "text": "我不知道该如何回应他的好意。也许她说的有道理,但我还没有做好准备。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "犹豫不决",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.82
    },
    {
      "id": 203,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_203_855b.wav",
      "text": "我跟他交流不多。纳维莱特说他值得信赖,所以我想他大概是个好人吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静中略带信任",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 5.75
    },
    {
      "id": 86,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0086.wav",
      "text": "哦,对了,以前还收到过她寄来的茶,味道不错。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "轻松回忆",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.95
    },
    {
      "id": 204,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_204_066a.wav",
      "text": "在我印象里,克洛琳德平时不喜交谈。当她几次站在我的身旁,保护我的安全,我对她非常信任。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静信任",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 8.02
    },
    {
      "id": 206,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_206_c929.wav",
      "text": "我还真有一点想念她。不过现在没什么去见他的理由了。对了,下次邀请他来一起开茶会吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "略带遗憾的思念",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 8.74
    },
    {
      "id": 205,
      "filename": "voice_lib/manual_merged_205_fd1f.wav",
      "text": "对我的事感兴趣。哎哟,真没办法。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "无奈敷衍",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
      "id": 94,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0094.wav",
      "text": "毕竟我曾经也是丰丹最受关注的大明星嘛,每天都有无数记者挖空心思想要探听我的隐私,我可是有丰富的经验将他们拒之门外。当然,我并不打算将这些经验用在你的身上,你可以用足够好吃的点心来和我交换秘密。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "得意调侃",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 17.78
    },
    {
      "id": 95,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0095.wav",
      "text": "最近有人向我推荐了冲浪这项运动,我也去体验了一番。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "轻松愉悦",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0096.wav",
      "text": "在惊涛骇浪中保持平衡并不是一件容易的事情,但我很快就掌握了技巧,也许是因为我有这方面的天赋?总之,在海天相接的地方近距离地感受风雨浪是一件还不错的事情,你也可以试一试。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自信轻松",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 18.2
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0097.wav",
      "text": "有空的话,多和我讲讲旅行的见闻吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "期待分享",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
      "id": 98,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0098.wav",
      "text": "我挺喜欢听你讲那些稀奇古怪的故事。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "轻松愉悦",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0099.wav",
      "text": "怎么说呢?我很容易对各种事物产生兴趣,但用不了多久就会感到无聊。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "无奈自嘲",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.88
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0100.wav",
      "text": "或许热情这种东西,越容易产生,就越容易失去?跟你在一起时,我似乎能一直保持愉快的心情,真不可思议。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "温暖感慨",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 11.34
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0101.wav",
      "text": "最近我一直在想,过去我是不是有点亏待自己了?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "略带遗憾",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0102.wav",
      "text": "为了保持神明的矜持,几乎没有享受过生活。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "无奈遗憾",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0103.wav",
      "text": "所以最近我迷上了购物,买了好多新奇的宝贝,像什么七色炫彩茶包,全自动伸缩刀叉,海马砖用马鞍。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋分享",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 9.85
    },
    {
      "id": 104,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0104.wav",
      "text": "最后发现大部分东西都用不上,我全部送去剧团当演出道具了。奇怪,出款前我明明觉得这些很有用的。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "无奈自嘲",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 11.23
    },
    {
      "id": 105,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0105.wav",
      "text": "人们很喜欢谈论过去。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "客观陈述",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0106.wav",
      "text": "为那些逝去的美好感到惋惜。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "惋惜怀念",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
      "id": 107,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0107.wav",
      "text": "也很喜欢谈论未来,仿佛为了缥缈的明天可以牺牲一切。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "深沉感慨",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
      "id": 108,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0108.wav",
      "text": "我并不认同他们的做法。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "不认同的质疑",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
      "id": 109,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0109.wav",
      "text": "但也感到非常羡慕。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "羡慕交织",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0110.wav",
      "text": "因为我曾经生活在既没有过去,",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "深沉失落",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
      "id": 111,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0111.wav",
      "text": "也没有未来的世界。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "绝望低沉",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
      "id": 112,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0112.wav",
      "text": "为了应对那种恐慌,我尝试塑造并扮演了一个更坚强、更像神明的自己。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "伪装坚强",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.37
    },
    {
      "id": 113,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0113.wav",
      "text": "几百年的时间过去,我曾扮演的形象逐渐与真实的自己融为一体。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "淡然融合",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 6.09
    },
    {
      "id": 114,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0114.wav",
      "text": "如今连我也无法分辨。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "迷茫失落",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
      "id": 115,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0115.wav",
      "text": "或许,也没有分辨的必要了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "无奈放弃",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
      "id": 116,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0116.wav",
      "text": "过去的种种经历组成了现在的我。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静反思",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
      "id": 117,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0117.wav",
      "text": "那场并不完美的演出,也是我最重要的一部分。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "坦然接纳",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
      "id": 118,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0118.wav",
      "text": "王后的容光还没有出续作吗?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静询问",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
      "id": 119,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0119.wav",
      "text": "真遗憾,这种正义战胜邪恶的经典作品,总是让人百看不厌。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "欣慰赞赏",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "id": 120,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0120.wav",
      "text": "今晚的通心粉,选什么叫好呢?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "日常询问",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
      "id": 121,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0121.wav",
      "text": "每个人都不会讨厌精致的糕点。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "愉悦肯定",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
      "id": 122,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0122.wav",
      "text": "但想要做到让我喜欢的程度,还需要多多努力才行。听好了,甜品就像歌剧,从选角到布景都需要花费心思,才能在最后的演出中大放异彩。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "挑剔不满",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 13.1
    },
    {
      "id": 123,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0123.wav",
      "text": "简单来说,我讨厌大部分创意材。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "直白反感",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
      "id": 124,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0124.wav",
      "text": "这些年我品尝过许多奇妙的料理,除了给我留下心理阴影外,毫无用处。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "无奈嘲讽",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 6.07
    },
    {
      "id": 125,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0125.wav",
      "text": "啊?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "意外疑惑",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 0.55
    },
    {
      "id": 126,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0126.wav",
      "text": "香味浓郁,口感细腻,没想到你对烹饪也有研究。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "惊喜赞赏",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.53
    },
    {
      "id": 127,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0127.wav",
      "text": "很有品位嘛。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "赞赏调侃",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": 128,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0128.wav",
      "text": "太普通了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平淡无感",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
      "id": 129,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0129.wav",
      "text": "这种缺乏特色的料理,得不到我的认可。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "轻蔑不屑",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
      "id": 131,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0131.wav",
      "text": "你平时只吃这些吗?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "略带质疑",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
      "id": 133,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0133.wav",
      "text": "我的通心粉分你一些好了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "慷慨分享",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
      "id": 134,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0134.wav",
      "text": "生日快乐!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "欢快祝福",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
      "id": 136,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0136.wav",
      "text": "作为生日礼物,这张票给你。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "温暖祝福",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
      "id": 137,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0137.wav",
      "text": "这可是欢乐日的头等座哦!记得过来看!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋邀请",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
      "id": 138,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0138.wav",
      "text": "你问我欢乐日是什么?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "好奇询问",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
      "id": 139,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0139.wav",
      "text": "唉,本来还想留一点惊喜的。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "略带遗憾",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
      "id": 140,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0140.wav",
      "text": "这是我亲自排练的一场歌剧,内容嘛,是很多人聚集在一起,为某个重要的人做庆贺。这么说你应该明白了吧?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自豪欢庆",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 9.2
    },
    {
      "id": 141,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0141.wav",
      "text": "一定要来啊!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "热情邀请",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 0.91
    },
    {
      "id": 142,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0142.wav",
      "text": "神之眼用起来还真不太习惯。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "厌",
        "complex": "略带无奈",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
      "id": 143,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0143.wav",
      "text": "你来教教我吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "温和邀请",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 0.98
    },
    {
      "id": 144,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0144.wav",
      "text": "啊,差点忘了,你也没用过神之眼啊。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "略带遗憾",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 3.96
    },
    {
      "id": 145,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0145.wav",
      "text": "靠自己锻炼得到的力量果然很充实。多谢了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "满足感激",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.9
    },
    {
      "id": 146,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0146.wav",
      "text": "渐入佳境,不愧是我,在任何情况下都能展现出闪耀的一面。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自信得意",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 7.13
    },
    {
      "id": 147,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0147.wav",
      "text": "没想到你会对我的事这么上心。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "欣慰感激",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.17
    },
    {
      "id": 148,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0148.wav",
      "text": "这是否意味着,你仍然需要我的力量呢?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "试探性询问",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
      "id": 149,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0149.wav",
      "text": "然而如今的我……",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "失落感慨",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
      "id": 150,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0150.wav",
      "text": "或许无法给你足够的回报。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "愧疚遗憾",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
      "id": 151,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0151.wav",
      "text": "你说看中的是我本人?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "怀疑试探",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
      "id": 152,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0152.wav",
      "text": "既然这样,就让你我共同出演我们的未来吧!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "憧憬期待",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
      "id": 157,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0157.wav",
      "text": "光芒啊!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惊",
        "complex": "惊喜赞叹",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 0.95
    },
    {
      "id": 158,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0158.wav",
      "text": "为你献上!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "热情洋溢",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
      "id": 159,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0159.wav",
      "text": "让世界热闹起来吧!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "欢快激昂",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
      "id": 160,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0160.wav",
      "text": "闪耀时刻!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋自豪",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
      "id": 161,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0161.wav",
      "text": "欢唱!以我之名!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "激昂欢庆",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
      "id": 162,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0162.wav",
      "text": "意外之喜,就像蛋糕上的王冠。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "惊喜愉悦",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
      "id": 163,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0163.wav",
      "text": "收下吧。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静给予",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 0.72
    },
    {
      "id": 164,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0164.wav",
      "text": "我准许了。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "平静许可",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
      "id": 165,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0165.wav",
      "text": "有趣的东西,当然是越读越好。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "愉悦分享",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
      "id": 166,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0166.wav",
      "text": "总之,先休战。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "冷静提议",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
      "id": 167,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0167.wav",
      "text": "情况不妙啊。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "担忧不安",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
      "id": 168,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0168.wav",
      "text": "救命啊!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "惊恐呼救",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
      "id": 169,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0169.wav",
      "text": "现实下我的实力!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "怒",
        "complex": "强烈宣示",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 1.39
    },
    {
      "id": 170,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0170.wav",
      "text": "换我登场啦!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "兴奋自信",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
      "id": 171,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0171.wav",
      "text": "算是一场解脱。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "释然平静",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
      "id": 172,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0172.wav",
      "text": "我还是没能做到。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "失落沮丧",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
      "id": 173,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0173.wav",
      "text": "别看我,丢人的样子。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "哀",
        "complex": "羞愧难当",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
      "id": 174,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0174.wav",
      "text": "干什么?",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "平",
        "complex": "中性询问",
        "intensity": "Low"
      },
      "duration": 1.31
    },
    {
      "id": 175,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0175.wav",
      "text": "别打了!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "惧",
        "complex": "惊恐哀求",
        "intensity": "High"
      },
      "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
      "id": 176,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0176.wav",
      "text": "果然还是离不开我啊。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "得意调侃",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
      "id": 177,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0177.wav",
      "text": "希望是一次尽兴的旅途。",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "期待愉悦",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
      "id": 178,
      "filename": "voice_lib/char_66ff5e94_0178.wav",
      "text": "瞧好了!",
      "emotion": {
        "primary": "喜",
        "complex": "自信展示",
        "intensity": "Medium"
      },
      "duration": 0.84
    }
  ]
}